The term '''Nica''' is an [[Toponymy|toponym]] used for [[Nicaragua]]ns or of Nicaraguan heritage. This term is highly used in [[Costa Rica]] referring to the Nicaraguans or of Nicaraguan heritage. In Costa Rica, this term is usually used in a derrogatory manner.

